Cell["\<\
VisualizeEuler::usage =
\t\"VisualizeEuler[{\[Alpha]PL,\[Beta]PL,\[Gamma]PL}] draws two axis systems, \
the lab axis system (thin lines), and an axis system P related to it by the \
Euler angles {\[Alpha]PL,\[Beta]PL,\[Gamma]PL} (thick lines)\";\
\>", "Input",
 PageWidth->WindowWidth,
 InitializationCell->True,
